## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js >= 20
- pnpm 10.28.0+
- Python 3.12+ (optional, for Python packages)
- uv (optional, for Python package management)

### Installation

```bash
pnpm install
```

### Development

```bash
pnpm dev
```

### Build

```bash
pnpm build
```

### Test

```bash
pnpm test
```

### Lint

```bash
pnpm lint
```

